<div id='main'>
	<h1>Is my blood pressure too high?</h1>
	<p>Thank you.</p><br />
	<% if @average_sysbp > 129 or @average_diabp > 80 %>
		<p>Your readings so far show that you may have high blood pressure...</p>
	<% else %>
		<p>Your readings so far show that you have normal blood pressure...</p>
	<% end %>
	<br />
	<p>... however, to get a true picture of what your blood pressure is like we need to take more readings like this over the next 4 days. Also, some other illnesses can change what is considered to be a healthy blood pressure - we will give you expert, personalised advice based on your individual health.</p>
	<br />
	<% if !user_signed_in? %>
		<p>Sign up so you can check your blood pressure over the next 4 days and receive free personalised advice on how best to control it. We cover everything from lifestyle advice through to supplying prescriptions for medications.</p>
		<div id='sign_up'>
			<%= render :partial => 'devise/registrations/new' %>
		</div>
	<% end %>
</div>

<div id='average_bp'>
	<%= render :partial => 'average_bp', :locals => {:avsys => @average_sysbp, :avdia => @average_diabp, :bppos => @bp_position} %>
</div>
